  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Compete with friends or team up to deliver the most gifts</strong></h2><strong>Chaotic platforming. Fast paced PvP combat. Diverse arenas filled with traps and hazards.<br>A thrilling experience that will surely (maybe, but probably not) ruin friendships.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 Game Modes - Delivery and Brawl<br></li><li> 14 Arena Levels<br></li><li> 13 Unique Power-ups<br></li><li> 2-4 Player Local Multiplayer <u><strong>(Controllers are required for each player in local multiplayer)</strong></u></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deploy an Arsenal of Ridiculous Power-ups</strong></h2><br><strong>Fireball</strong> - Fast. Reliable. Just don't miss.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/6a5685d4c959e859a6f61588037cef6f.poster.avif?t=1701428789\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/6a5685d4c959e859a6f61588037cef6f.webm?t=1701428789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/6a5685d4c959e859a6f61588037cef6f.mp4?t=1701428789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Hammer Swirl</strong> - Big tools for tiny hands. Nailed it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/8bb1c89d12ed80a38f81fa2d28f181f2.poster.avif?t=1701428789\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/8bb1c89d12ed80a38f81fa2d28f181f2.webm?t=1701428789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/8bb1c89d12ed80a38f81fa2d28f181f2.mp4?t=1701428789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Cluster Duck</strong> - Quack, Quack, BOOM<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/82e1df9495be60682229898a6bbee2f4.poster.avif?t=1701428789\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/82e1df9495be60682229898a6bbee2f4.webm?t=1701428789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061100/extras/82e1df9495be60682229898a6bbee2f4.mp4?t=1701428789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>...and many more!</strong>",
